  "body": "| Driver                                                                           | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |\n| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Drivers that use a JRE (Java Runtime Environment) or JDK (Java Development Kit)' | Due to an issue with TLS (Transport Layer Security) 1.3 support in the Java JDK (Java Development Kit)' (JDK-8236039), upgrade the JDK (Java Development Kit)' that supports the driver you use to connect to Atlas.Minimum versions of the JDK (Java Development Kit)' include:14u-cpuJDK-824910714.0.2JDK-824795413.0.3JDK-824151511.0.8-oracleJDK-823850411.0.7JDK-82373878u261JDK-8243759emb-8u261JDK-8247097To learn more about support for TLS (Transport Layer Security) 1.3 in Java-based languages, libraries, and drivers, see:MongoDB Java, Reactive Streams, and Scala DriversScalaKafka |",
